# Per-machine diagnostics and captures.
.env
_work/
**/logs/
**/evidence/*
!**/evidence/README.md
**/experiments.tsv

# Live configuration/save snapshots may contain account and machine data.
**/configs/

# Generated binaries, locks, cloned source trees, and isolated Proton prefixes.
**/runtime/
**/source/
**/prefixes/

# Re-download these from the pinned URLs/checksums in installer scripts.
**/tool-downloads/

# Locally captured third-party/community material.
**/protondb.txt

# Common transient files.
__pycache__/
*.pyc
_pages-src/
_pages-mkdocs.yml
_site/
*.log
*.out
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.core
core
